#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.weibull"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Weibull distribution."
msgstr "从威布尔分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:3 of
msgid ""
"Draw samples from a 1-parameter Weibull distribution with the given shape"
" parameter `a`."
msgstr "从给定形状参数 `a` 的单参数威布尔分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:6 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"X = (-ln(U))^{1/a}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:8 of
msgid "Here, U is drawn from the uniform distribution over (0,1]."
msgstr "其中，U 是从 (0,1] 上的均匀分布中抽取的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:10 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The more common 2-parameter Weibull, including a scale parameter "
":math:`\\lambda` is just :math:`X = \\lambda(-ln(U))^{1/a}`."
msgstr ""
"更常见的两参数威布尔分布包含尺度参数 :math:`\\lambda`，其表达式为 :math:`"
"X = \\lambda(-ln(U))^{1/a}`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:13 of
msgid "Shape of the distribution. Should be greater than zero."
msgstr "分布的形状参数。应大于零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:15 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``a`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``mt.array(a).size`` samples "
"are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个"
"样本。如果 size 是 ``None``（默认值），当 ``a`` 是标量时返回单个值。否则"
"，抽取 ``mt.array(a).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:20 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:22 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:24 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:27 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized Weibull distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的威布尔分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:30 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`scipy.stats.weibull_max`, :py:obj:`scipy.stats.weibull_min`, "
":py:obj:`scipy.stats.genextreme`, :py:obj:`gumbel`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:34 of
msgid ""
"The Weibull (or Type III asymptotic extreme value distribution for "
"smallest values, SEV Type III, or Rosin-Rammler distribution) is one of a"
" class of Generalized Extreme Value (GEV) distributions used in modeling "
"extreme value problems. This class includes the Gumbel and Frechet "
"distributions."
msgstr ""
"威布尔分布（或最小值的第三类渐近极值分布，SEV Type III，或 Rosin-Rammler "
"分布）是广义极值 (GEV) 分布中用于建模极值问题的一类分布。此类分布包括 "
"Gumbel 分布和 Frechet 分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:40 of
msgid "The probability density for the Weibull distribution is"
msgstr "威布尔分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:42 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"p(x) = \\frac{a}\n"
"{\\lambda}(\\frac{x}{\\lambda})^{a-1}e^{-(x/\\lambda)^a},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:45 of
msgid "where :math:`a` is the shape and :math:`\\lambda` the scale."
msgstr "其中 :math:`a` 是形状参数，:math:`\\lambda` 是尺度参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:47 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The function has its peak (the mode) at "
":math:`\\lambda(\\frac{a-1}{a})^{1/a}`."
msgstr "该函数在其峰值（众数）处为 :math:`\\lambda(\\frac{a-1}{a})^{1/a}`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:50 of
msgid ""
"When ``a = 1``, the Weibull distribution reduces to the exponential "
"distribution."
msgstr "当 ``a = 1`` 时，威布尔分布退化为指数分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:54 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:55 of
msgid ""
"Waloddi Weibull, Royal Technical University, Stockholm, 1939 \"A "
"Statistical Theory Of The Strength Of Materials\", "
"Ingeniorsvetenskapsakademiens Handlingar Nr 151, 1939, Generalstabens "
"Litografiska Anstalts Forlag, Stockholm."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:59 of
msgid ""
"Waloddi Weibull, \"A Statistical Distribution Function of Wide "
"Applicability\", Journal Of Applied Mechanics ASME Paper 1951."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:62 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Weibull distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weibull_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:66 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:67 of
msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.weibull.weibull:74 of
msgid ""
"Display the histogram of the samples, along with the probability density "
"function:"
msgstr "显示样本的直方图以及概率密度函数："

